data.description: looking for a home for your horses....This is it! Property has a 80x160 riding ring, 60' round pen, 4 paddocks and four matted stalls in the stable. Two water hydrants close to horse area. Seller says that riding trails would be easily established in wooded area by stream. Garage/workshop has attached tack and feed room. Workshop has been prepared to allow for welding or auto repair due to installation of fire retardant drywall and fire-rated spray foam insulation. Garage has its one separate 100 amp service while service to main house was updated to 200 amp service. Farmhouse includes main floor laundry/pantry/mudroom to remove boots etc. from coming in from the stable. Eat in kitchen with newer flooring, livingroom/dining area. Primary bedroom has a propane fireplace and access to Full Bath from bedroom and hallway. Main level has central air and forced air heat.  Upstairs there are two bedrooms and basebaord heat. Seller is leaving AC units for upstairs. Yard is fully fenced as appropriate to accomodate horses.
